{"tid":362998,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【雙學三子入獄】外媒廣泛報道　憂北京踐踏香港自由","createTime":"2017-08-17T10:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-18T10:04:51.000Z","uid":48083,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"eff98894a79754a95d0121778f04d1eedbac5b42","tid":362998,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:28:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/newshead-18_kIrwL_1200x0.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fnewshead-18_kIrwL_1200x0.png&d=6ok3VQmsvZppOWXrlQlUTkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=9de47a06\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fnewshead-18_kIrwL_1200x0.png&h=12251ae4\" target=\"_blank\">https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/newshead-18_kIrwL_1200x0.png</a><br />\n<br />\n重奪公民廣場案的刑期覆核今日宣判，「雙學三子」的香港眾志主席羅冠聰、秘書長黃之鋒及學聯前秘書長周永康，被判囚 6 至 8 個月，即時收監。事件獲外國傳媒廣泛報道，更成為英國《衛報》及美國 CNN 的頭條，而英國《每日電訊報》則表示，裁決結果令人憂慮北京踐踏香港自由。<br />\n<br />\n涉及三年前 926 公民廣場案的羅冠聰、黃之鋒及周永康，早前分別被判社會服務令及緩刑一年，惟遭律政司申請刑期覆核。上訴庭今日就覆核作出裁決，三人分別判囚 6 至 8 個月，即時收監。<br />\n<br />\n事件獲多個外國傳媒報道，其中英國《每日電訊報》的報道提到，中國大陸曾於主權移交前承諾維持香港自由，惟今日的裁決結果「令人關注北京當局踐踏當年承諾」。<br />\n<br />\n英國《衛報》及美國 CNN 將消息列於新聞網頁的頭條位置，其中《衛報》引述國際特赦組織香港分會總幹事區美寶（Mabel Au）指，判決含有「政治代價」的意味；並援引佛羅里達州聯邦參議員馬可&middot;魯比奧（Marco Antonio Rubio）發出的聲明，批評裁決反映北京試圖打擊香港新一代的民主運動。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%9B%99%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84-%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E5%BB%A3%E6%B3%9B%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93-%E6%86%82%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%B8%90%E8%B8%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%259B%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%2584-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%25B3%259B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593-%25E6%2586%2582%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E8%25B8%2590%25E8%25B8%258F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%2F&d=6ok3VQmsvZppOWXrlQlUTkjIoeaDRyeQRMy%2FzT52C%2Fo%3D&h=97a7d156\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%259B%2599%25E5%25AD%25B8%25E4%25B8%2589%25E5%25AD%2590%25E5%2585%25A5%25E7%258D%2584-%25E5%25A4%2596%25E5%25AA%2592%25E5%25BB%25A3%25E6%25B3%259B%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E9%2581%2593-%25E6%2586%2582%25E5%258C%2597%25E4%25BA%25AC%25E8%25B8%2590%25E8%25B8%258F%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2587%25AA%25E7%2594%25B1%2F&h=09389c5b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%9B%99%E5%AD%B8%E4%B8%89%E5%AD%90%E5%85%A5%E7%8D%84-%E5%A4%96%E5%AA%92%E5%BB%A3%E6%B3%9B%E5%A0%B1%E9%81%93-%E6%86%82%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC%E8%B8%90%E8%B8%8F%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1/</a>"},{"pid":"870c55e86579c87fd3e5cf54918089e945dfe4f5","tid":362998,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T10:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/newshead-18_kIrwL_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2Fnewshead-18_kIrwL_1200x0.png&h=bc83d3c6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"067a7fa26b7c6768ac99bb2ec41a3d903059653a","tid":362998,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:10:43.000Z","msg":"快點打救香港"},{"pid":"9cd2aaf7bc6895ea07386e58a7d96250f81a9fa0","tid":362998,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:17:31.000Z","msg":"垃場新聞=雨革失蹤"},{"pid":"fe92aa66a19883619a402ae7527174c659ee2860","tid":362998,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:21:10.000Z","msg":"憂乜鬼，嘛一日踐踏緊囉"},{"pid":"e269ffad18460021bbf5d19ebfa9c4beb16353e2","tid":362998,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-17T13:29:11.000Z","msg":"終於引起外國關注"},{"pid":"149c079be0c836d63be0affb1724d2a6